  m_text: "Cycle of Life (Conway's Game of Life)\n\nRules:\n\n-Birth Rule: An empty,
    or \u201Cdead,\u201D cell with precisely three \u201Clive\u201D neighbors (full
    cells) becomes live.\r\n\r\n-Death Rule: A live cell with zero or one neighbors
    dies of isolation; a live cell with four or more neighbors dies of overcrowding.\r\n\r\n-Survival
    Rule: A live cell with two or three neighbors remains alive.\n\n\n--------"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
